    Call LECTEXTRA([M:FAS1]ZIASACC,"GACCOUNT","DESTRA",num$([M:FPC]COA(max(0,[M:FPC]IASLEDTYP-1))),num$([M:FAS1]IASACC(indice))) From ATEXTRA
    Affzo [M:FAS1]25
  Else
    # Classé pour vente
